Context()->texStrings;
SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR
$SOL
With \( a_n = $an \), 
\[ \sqrt[n]{a_n} = \sqrt[n]{$an} = \frac{$num}{$den} \] and \[ \lim_{n \to \infty} \sqrt[n]{a_n}  $result. \]

Therefore, $FinalState

